    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你们一定都听说过他的故事，，，，，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果没有听说过，那我现在给你们编一个，，，，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289550/extras/eaff8d93238053c518037b6c57e89ed5.avif?t=1759313441\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在丧尸遍地的世界，无数幸存者听到了广播，动身寻找传说中的避难所：伊甸园。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这其中就有你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但是路途总是充满艰难险阻的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各种各样的丧尸阻挡在你前进的道路上，然而，除了面对这些已知的威胁，还有更多的未知等待着你，。为此，你需要：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小心谨慎的前行，最好不要发出一丁点声音，它们潜伏在黑夜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289550/extras/5fb858257e5a4579ec05bfe35cca65f0.avif?t=1759313441\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289550/extras_big/5fb858257e5a4579ec05bfe35cca65f0.avif?t=1759313441 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >招集你的队友，协同作战，在必要的时刻对四面八方而来的敌人迎头痛击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289550/extras/3e8717156fae633ba8cefdd39ed80dd0.avif?t=1759313441\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289550/extras_big/3e8717156fae633ba8cefdd39ed80dd0.avif?t=1759313441 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集各种各样的道具，比如手雷，枪械，炸药等，在适合时候使用它们，可以让任务变得更加轻松。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >营救被困人员，拾取可用的武器装备，为我们的生存赢得更多的希望。</p>",
